      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VIERATA (1) just ran into one better over this track and trip on debut and will have derived a stack of benefit from that race day experience. Was well in the betting on that occasion and where there's smoke there's fire. Rates the testing material from the inside marble. HEART OF VIENNA (3) has been thereabouts in both career outings to date and gets some weight relief with the 2kg claim. Looms as the main danger. MONDAY CLOSE (2) just missed the frame at Cairns last time out and maps ideally for this from gate three. Top-three aspirations. OSTUNI (8) has gotten better with each run and looks to be improving with racing. In the mix. WORTHY BELLE (5) is facing the starter for the first time but won't need to be a superstar to be competitive against this lot. Keep very safe.",
